1
00:00:19,162 --> 00:00:24,349
笙ｪThe whole world is lit up笙ｪ

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
笙ｪBecause you exist笙ｪ

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
笙ｪYou're always笙ｪ

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
笙ｪSomewhere close, flying with me笙ｪ

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
笙ｪGo to where the wind blows笙ｪ

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
笙ｪHold tight笙ｪ

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
笙ｪTo the ray of light that belongs to us笙ｪ

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:48,032
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 20=

9
00:01:00,862 --> 00:01:03,495
笙ｪThe wind blows across the wilderness笙ｪ

10
00:01:03,762 --> 00:01:06,820
笙ｪClouds at the end of the world笙ｪ

11
00:01:07,512 --> 00:01:09,786
笙ｪLike your silhouette笙ｪ

12
00:01:09,787 --> 00:01:13,707
笙ｪSlowly swallowed by the sunset笙ｪ

13
00:01:14,012 --> 00:01:17,411
笙ｪI'm standing in笙ｪ

14
00:01:17,412 --> 00:01:20,382
笙ｪThe corner of abandoned time笙ｪ

15
00:01:20,650 --> 00:01:23,061
笙ｪI watch the stars in your eyes笙ｪ

16
00:01:23,062 --> 00:01:26,457
笙ｪFall one by one笙ｪ

17
00:01:27,512 --> 00:01:32,539
笙ｪRain drifts over
an old boat at a lonely pier笙ｪ

18
00:01:32,540 --> 00:01:34,179
You knew it all along, didn't you?

19
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:36,299
笙ｪLike your whispers笙ｪ

20
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:37,299
About our origins.

21
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,058
笙ｪBeing gently brushed by waves笙ｪ

22
00:01:39,059 --> 00:01:41,299
You've known
that I'm not the Mu family's daughter.

23
00:01:41,419 --> 00:01:42,860
And you've also known

24
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:45,500
that you are the heir to Mu Group.

25
00:01:47,275 --> 00:01:48,659
笙ｪWaiting for the moonlight笙ｪ

26
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:50,218
Then, why didn't you tell me?

27
00:01:50,219 --> 00:01:53,939
笙ｪTo dye the path into amber笙ｪ

28
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:56,459
You watched me
being kept in the dark like a fool.

29
00:01:56,660 --> 00:01:58,220
So you found it amusing?

30
00:01:59,619 --> 00:02:02,379
Watching me fight Mu Group,
which has nothing to do with me,

31
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:04,138
tooth and nail against Xu Mingzhu?

32
00:02:04,139 --> 00:02:05,624
Does it make you happy?

33
00:02:05,625 --> 00:02:09,757
笙ｪAt least this wind once filled my void笙ｪ

34
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:11,699
I did know before.

35
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:14,979
But I really didn't know

36
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,419
how to tell you.

37
00:02:16,712 --> 00:02:18,179
笙ｪA journey with no end笙ｪ

38
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:19,218
I never even wanted

39
00:02:19,219 --> 00:02:21,099
to be the heir to Mu Group.

40
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:24,300
But if this is
the only way to protect you,

41
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:26,300
I'm willing to do anything.

42
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,259
Protect me?

43
00:02:34,062 --> 00:02:35,658
笙ｪThe wind blows across the wilderness笙ｪ

44
00:02:35,659 --> 00:02:37,186
Your so-called protection

45
00:02:37,187 --> 00:02:40,245
笙ｪClouds at the end of the world笙ｪ

46
00:02:40,379 --> 00:02:42,900
was to treat me like an idiot,

47
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:46,218
笙ｪSlowly swallowed by the sunset笙ｪ

48
00:02:46,219 --> 00:02:48,259
which led me to end up like this,

49
00:02:50,659 --> 00:02:52,020
with absolutely nothing.

50
00:02:54,012 --> 00:02:56,579
笙ｪI watch the stars in your eyes笙ｪ

51
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:57,740
Stop following me.

52
00:03:01,112 --> 00:03:04,449
笙ｪPerhaps you are a relic
from my past life笙ｪ

53
00:03:04,450 --> 00:03:08,757
笙ｪDestined only to be watched,
never touched笙ｪ

54
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,979
Who gave you permission
to touch my things?

55
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:18,419
Madam said that you are no longer
the daughter of the Mu family.

56
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:20,299
We should clear these things out early

57
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,419
so they don't take up space.

58
00:03:21,420 --> 00:03:23,099
Don't push me too far.

59
00:03:24,099 --> 00:03:25,220
Where is Xu Mingzhu?

60
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,500
Tell her to come out.

61
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:30,500
What's wrong?

62
00:03:31,819 --> 00:03:33,019
Tearing the house down?

63
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:33,979
Mu Zhiyu,

64
00:03:34,539 --> 00:03:36,939
you are no longer
the daughter of the Mu family.

65
00:03:36,980 --> 00:03:38,300
Do you still want to linger here?

66
00:03:39,362 --> 00:03:42,299
I gave you a way out,
so don't be ungrateful.

67
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:43,979
Who's really the ungrateful one?

68
00:03:53,387 --> 00:03:56,110
Mu Zhiyu is indeed
no longer the daughter of the Mu family.

69
00:03:56,337 --> 00:03:58,749
but she is the rightful
madam of the Mu family.

70
00:04:00,099 --> 00:04:01,020
Now,

71
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:01,979
take these things

72
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,500
to her room immediately.

73
00:04:06,099 --> 00:04:07,300
Shen Jibai,

74
00:04:07,379 --> 00:04:09,900
do you still respect me
as the madam of the Mu family?

75
00:04:11,059 --> 00:04:12,818
No matter what, I am your elder.

76
00:04:12,819 --> 00:04:14,300
Do you think I'm dead?

77
00:04:15,619 --> 00:04:16,659
Xu Mingzhu,

78
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:20,020
I haven't settled the score
regarding my father yet.

79
00:04:20,179 --> 00:04:22,419
You'd better watch your own back.

80
00:04:29,487 --> 00:04:30,727
(Don't get cocky.)

81
00:04:30,979 --> 00:04:32,939
(So what if you have the upper hand?)

82
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:34,179
(Just you wait.)

83
00:04:49,020 --> 00:04:50,179
Shen Jibai,

84
00:04:51,179 --> 00:04:52,739
I told you not to follow me.

85
00:04:53,099 --> 00:04:54,940
Why did you bring me here?

86
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:56,459
I brought you here,

87
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:58,340
of course, to give you...

88
00:05:01,098 --> 00:05:02,499
I'm warning you, don't try anything.

89
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,299
笙ｪThe fragmented, peaceful笙ｪ

90
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:09,019
笙ｪTiniest dream笙ｪ

91
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,139
In your eyes,

92
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:12,580
am I really such a scoundrel
who takes advantage of people?

93
00:05:13,139 --> 00:05:16,440
In your current state, you probably don't want
to stay in the Mu house anymore, right?

94
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,538
Take a hot bath first,

95
00:05:17,539 --> 00:05:18,979
and don't think about anything else.

96
00:05:19,299 --> 00:05:20,499
I'll go run the water for you.

97
00:05:22,312 --> 00:05:24,211
笙ｪBecause you appeared笙ｪ

98
00:05:24,212 --> 00:05:26,286
笙ｪMy world becomes hazy笙ｪ

99
00:05:26,287 --> 00:05:28,549
笙ｪAdvancing while retreating笙ｪ

100
00:05:28,550 --> 00:05:30,749
笙ｪGuessing how you feel笙ｪ

101
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,749
笙ｪYou'll never understand笙ｪ

102
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:34,639
笙ｪThese random emotions笙ｪ

103
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:37,139
笙ｪAre controlled by you笙ｪ

104
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:37,900
It's ready.

105
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:38,924
Please.

106
00:05:38,925 --> 00:05:41,298
笙ｪWill you care about
my feelings once more?笙ｪ

107
00:05:41,299 --> 00:05:42,460
What about you?

108
00:05:42,539 --> 00:05:45,059
I have my own things to do, of course.

109
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:46,140
Don't worry.

110
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:50,479
笙ｪNot daring to think too much笙ｪ

111
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:55,699
笙ｪTo see if you like me笙ｪ

112
00:05:55,700 --> 00:05:59,719
笙ｪWill you occasionally
wait for me by your phone?笙ｪ

113
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:03,839
笙ｪWill the music you share be about me?笙ｪ

114
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:07,399
笙ｪNot daring to say too much笙ｪ

115
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:13,440
笙ｪPerhaps you already
understand my heart笙ｪ

116
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:36,111
笙ｪWatching you walk forward笙ｪ

117
00:06:36,112 --> 00:06:38,552
笙ｪLike a passing spark笙ｪ

118
00:06:39,179 --> 00:06:41,260
(Mu Zhiyu,)

119
00:06:41,339 --> 00:06:42,979
(is your last name really Mu?)

120
00:06:43,339 --> 00:06:46,099
(My identity as the daughter
of the Mu family all these years)

121
00:06:46,419 --> 00:06:48,619
(turns out to be all a swap conspiracy.)

122
00:06:49,099 --> 00:06:50,499
(A lie.)

123
00:06:51,099 --> 00:06:52,859
(Now, it's over.)

124
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:55,220
(The identity is gone.)

125
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,700
(Then, who are you exactly?)

126
00:06:58,219 --> 00:06:59,099
(Right.)

127
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:02,179
(Who am I?)

128
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:05,299
(Do I have parents or relatives?)

129
00:07:07,779 --> 00:07:09,020
(In this world,)

130
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:11,499
(is there anyone who will care for me,)

131
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,700
(love me,)

132
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:15,179
(and treat me with sincerity?)

133
00:07:16,475 --> 00:07:19,699
笙ｪNo need to say too much笙ｪ

134
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:28,040
笙ｪI think
I already understand your heart笙ｪ

135
00:07:37,659 --> 00:07:38,459
Done?

136
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:40,259
Come and try the pasta I made.

137
00:07:40,260 --> 00:07:42,659
I spent a long time on it.
You're not allowed to say it's bad.

138
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:16,419
How is it? Does it taste good?

139
00:08:20,739 --> 00:08:21,859
It's good.

140
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:27,338
It seems I didn't do a good job.

141
00:08:27,339 --> 00:08:28,580
I should just throw it away.

142
00:08:28,659 --> 00:08:29,979
You don't have to be polite.

143
00:08:33,459 --> 00:08:35,099
It's really quite delicious.

144
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:38,060
It's just

145
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:40,499
that right now...

146
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:42,259
Are you still mad at me?

147
00:08:45,987 --> 00:08:49,857
笙ｪIn the lonely night笙ｪ

148
00:08:50,779 --> 00:08:52,779
I have no right to be mad at you.

149
00:08:53,819 --> 00:08:55,379
You're a victim too.

150
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,460
If it weren't for me,

151
00:08:58,779 --> 00:08:59,979
and if this

152
00:09:00,299 --> 00:09:02,060
life-swapping incident hadn't happened,

153
00:09:02,939 --> 00:09:03,940
perhaps

154
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:07,820
you would have a much better life now.

155
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,619
And I

156
00:09:11,459 --> 00:09:12,899
stole your life.

157
00:09:12,900 --> 00:09:14,540
It wasn't like that.

158
00:09:16,059 --> 00:09:17,739
You certainly have
a right to be mad at me.

159
00:09:18,819 --> 00:09:21,538
It's because I hadn't figured out
how to tell you about our origins,

160
00:09:21,539 --> 00:09:23,379
which allowed
Xu Mingzhu to make such a fuss.

161
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:27,019
You didn't steal my life either.

162
00:09:29,059 --> 00:09:30,339
No one could have

163
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,899
foreseen such a thing happening,

164
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:32,974
right?

165
00:09:32,975 --> 00:09:37,739
笙ｪFootsteps rush and linger笙ｪ

166
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,899
But now,

167
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:41,580
I'm no longer the heiress to Mu Group.

168
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:43,619
And I really don't know

169
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:45,700
the password for the inheritance.

170
00:09:46,539 --> 00:09:47,540
So,

171
00:09:47,939 --> 00:09:48,899
you

172
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:51,060
don't have to
force yourself to marry me.

173
00:09:51,179 --> 00:09:52,420
What do you mean?

174
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:55,418
Are you trying to abandon me

175
00:09:55,419 --> 00:09:56,660
at your most difficult time?

176
00:09:59,419 --> 00:10:01,779
I would never give up
the chance to stay by your side.

177
00:10:02,912 --> 00:10:06,061
笙ｪOn the platform笙ｪ

178
00:10:06,062 --> 00:10:10,695
笙ｪFootsteps rush and linger笙ｪ

179
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:11,899
Zhiyu,

180
00:10:12,939 --> 00:10:14,540
after everything that's happened,

181
00:10:14,860 --> 00:10:16,099
I'm certain now

182
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:19,818
that I will never
let go of your hand again.

183
00:10:19,819 --> 00:10:25,299
笙ｪI know I should offer you my blessings笙ｪ

184
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:29,899
笙ｪYet I stand still on the spot笙ｪ

185
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:35,124
笙ｪForgetting where I am supposed to stay笙ｪ

186
00:10:35,125 --> 00:10:41,032
笙ｪLost, counting down, it's over笙ｪ

187
00:10:41,062 --> 00:10:48,182
笙ｪOnly I am left staring at the window笙ｪ

188
00:11:06,412 --> 00:11:10,642
笙ｪLight comes beaming in笙ｪ

189
00:11:10,782 --> 00:11:15,151
笙ｪLanding on my skin笙ｪ

190
00:11:15,152 --> 00:11:19,642
笙ｪWarms the space you left behind笙ｪ

191
00:11:23,862 --> 00:11:27,801
笙ｪShadows move around笙ｪ

192
00:11:27,802 --> 00:11:32,411
笙ｪAwake, racing thoughts笙ｪ

193
00:11:32,412 --> 00:11:36,942
笙ｪTry to keep the memories safe笙ｪ

194
00:11:40,542 --> 00:11:46,332
笙ｪDon't slip away笙ｪ

195
00:11:48,782 --> 00:11:53,351
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

196
00:11:53,352 --> 00:11:57,751
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

197
00:11:57,752 --> 00:12:02,072
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

198
00:12:02,092 --> 00:12:06,072
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

199
00:12:06,542 --> 00:12:10,851
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

200
00:12:10,852 --> 00:12:15,181
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

201
00:12:15,182 --> 00:12:19,491
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

202
00:12:19,492 --> 00:12:25,642
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ
